Class AbstractMigrationQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tsgrp.migration.queue.AbstractMigrationQueue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MigrationQueue
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JdbcMigrationQueue, MigrationQueueVirtual, MigrationQueueWatchFolder, PumaJdbcMigrationQueue

    public abstract class AbstractMigrationQueue
extends java.lang.Object
implements MigrationQueue
    Implements the non-implementaton specific queue methods (e.g., agnostic status-related methods, firing events).
